Romanization

Haluga tto hansum gat-eun nal
Hansum-i ne nunmul gat-eun nal
Ileon nal balabomyeo
Apass-eul neoyeossneunde
Mosnan nae yogsim-i keojyeoseo
Neoui sum-i nae sum-ilan geol
Nan mollass-eo salang was you

Geunyeoneun son-eul jabneun geol joh-ahaeyo
Son-eul jab-eumyeon
Ma-eumkkaji tonghandaeyo
Changpihadan ping-gyelo mos jab-eun
Jogeuman geunyeo son-eul
Ttam-i nado nohji malgo
Deoug kkog jab-ajwoyo

